@Vic_Gill If you do go to the supermarket:

🚫 Keep at least 2m from others 
🧼 Wash your hands for 20 seconds after shopping
🛒 Avoid touching your face after handling shopping trolleys, baskets, packages and produce
💳 Use contactless payment methods

@Vic_Gill You could leave a note on your door asking drivers to ring the bell and step back

For unwrapped fresh goods wash thoroughly and leave to dry

Any risk would be the possible contamination of food or packaging

@Vic_Gill What about pubs? 🍺

Some bars are selling drinks to takeaway customers

https://t.co/a8HEp9kuvI https://t.co/vM4b1r7oDl

🍲 Empty the contents into a clean dish
🚮 Dispose of the packaging into a refuse bag
🧼👏 Wash your hands thoroughly 
🥄 Take food out of a container with a spoon 
🍽️ Eat it with a knife and fork

https://t.co/a8HEp9kuvI https://t.co/IuQmytepmu

https://t.co/a8HEp9kuvI https://t.co/wGs0GumlAq

🥪 Pret a Manger offer takeaways and online delivery
☕ M&S has reopened some cafes for takeaway
